WEBVTT

00:03:27.760 --> 00:03:30.609
"What about fluid dynamics?"

00:03:30.633 --> 00:03:33.232
Now, sleeping is delightful.

00:03:33.256 --> 00:03:36.364
My favorite -- I mean, you could be
upside down, right side up --

00:03:36.388 --> 00:03:39.360
my favorite: curled up
in a little ball and floating freely.

00:03:40.066 --> 00:03:42.335
Laundry? Nope.

00:03:42.359 --> 00:03:45.987
We load our dirty clothes
into an empty supply ship

00:03:46.011 --> 00:03:48.276
and send it off into space.

00:03:48.300 --> 00:03:49.471
The bathroom.

00:03:49.495 --> 00:03:50.887
Everyone wants to know.

00:03:50.911 --> 00:03:53.635
It's hard to understand,
so I made a little video,

00:03:53.659 --> 00:03:56.119
because I wanted kids to understand

00:03:56.143 --> 00:03:59.040
that the principle of vacuum saves the day

00:03:59.064 --> 00:04:02.143
and that just a gentle breeze
helps everything go